<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Musafir</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  <div style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <div style="background-color: #ff5733; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="color: #fff; margin: 0;">Greetings from Musafir!</h1>
    </div>
    <div style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #555;">Hi <%= name %>,</p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #555;">Thank you for subscribing to Musafir's newsletter!</p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #555;">Stay tuned for exciting news, events, fairs, standups, and more happening in Surat.</p>
      <a href="https://musafir-main.vercel.app/explore" style="background-color: #ff5733; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px;">Explore Musafir</a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #aaa;">
      <p>You're receiving this email because you subscribed to Musafir's newsletter.</p>
      <p>If you wish to unsubscribe, <a href="#" style="color: #ff5733; text-decoration: none;">click here</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
